Canonical CDC Event Schema (CMWS)

1. Purpose

This schema standardizes all CDC events from CMWS into a unified structure for downstream processing and process mining. It ensures consistency across all schemas and source tables while preserving key workflow context.

The design is based on the recommendation that WORKFLOW_HISTORY is the primary event source, with additional enrichment from other tables. 


