2. Canonical Fields

Field Name	Description	Source Mapping

event_id	Unique identifier for each normalized event	Generated during transformation
schema_name	Schema in which the event occurred (used for cross-schema tracking)	Derived from CDC metadata (e.g., LRKPROD, COBPROD, EPRPROD)
case_id	Unique identifier of the workflow instance	document_id from source tables
activity	Business-readable event name (e.g., Moved, Assigned, Reserved)	Derived from workflow_event_cd and event_data fields
